1.0.0.name: wordpress/swtor-recruitment
1.0.0.description:
SWTOR Recruitment is an easy to use widget that lets your guild site's visitors know what classes/specializations you are recruiting.
It provides a single admin page to manage the recruitment status for both Empire and Republic factions.
At the widget page, you can run multiple instances of the widget, including both Empire and Republic at the same time if you are a dual faction guild. Can be set to display in English, French, or German.
